GameSparks,is,a,cloud,based,platform,that,provides,developers,with,the,tools,they,need,to,build,the,server,side,components,of,their,games,and,then,manage,them,as,a,service,post,launch,The,GameSparks,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,GameSparks,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,social,media,managing,in,app,purchases,and,managing,engagement